{"tid":1984730,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4/PC] Monster Hunter World: Iceborne [40] 巨鑽眠武刷爛輝","createTime":"2020-04-22T15:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T16:04:12.000Z","uid":142416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c75ca42bf7b926e3e93525ca5db220e4f5187af3","tid":1984730,"uid":142416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:59:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請盡量用不推文回覆</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44KX7Z6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44KX7Z6.png&h=f0e4d71c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3fVE17.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3fVE17.gif&h=5dac49b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwQhMhY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwQhMhY.jpg&h=22411729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins><strong>網上獵人經驗心得</strong></ins><br />\n<strong>Monster Hunter World官網</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.capcom.com%2Fmanual%2FMHW%2Fzh-hant%2Fps4&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=85037711\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4</a><br />\n<strong>中文Wiki</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhchinese.wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhchinese.wiki&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=d390f462\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhchinese.wiki</a>(無更新)<br />\n<strong>日本Wiki</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://mhwg.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhwg.org%2F&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=228d8d6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://mhwg.org/</a> (較常用)<br />\n<a href=\"https://game8.jp/mhw/196165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fmhw%2F196165&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=556e0213\" target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/mhw/196165</a><br />\n<strong>台灣網站教學</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;page=&amp;snA=136459&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26page%3D%26snA%3D136459%26last%3D&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=b4b34659\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;page=&amp;snA=136459&amp;last=</a><br />\n<strong>配裝模擬器 日中英文對照 Skill simulator</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://mhw.wiki-db.com/sim/?hl=zh-hant#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhw.wiki-db.com%2Fsim%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hant%23&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=a7e1095b\" target=\"_blank\">http://mhw.wiki-db.com/sim/?hl=zh-hant#</a><br />\n<strong><strong>配裝器使用教學</strong></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=05786&amp;snA=145099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D05786%26snA%3D145099&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=c6507e1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=05786&amp;snA=145099</a><br />\n<strong>傷害模擬器</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://kuroyonhon.com/mhw/d/dame.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkuroyonhon.com%2Fmhw%2Fd%2Fdame.php&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=d2ce8ee0\" target=\"_blank\">http://kuroyonhon.com/mhw/d/dame.php</a><br />\n<strong>***新手獵人Q&amp;A***</strong></div><br />\n<strong><ins>Q：玩咩武器好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：去鍛練場試手感，獵人冇廢裝。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咩武器高輸出？</ins></strong><br />\nA：十隻手指各有長短，用剋屬就可以。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：一開始用咩裝好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：防衛隊裝備就可以，夠用到G位。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：遊戲買左日版(或其他版) DLC要買咩版？</ins></strong><br />\nA：DLC要遊戲要相同地區先玩到。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：玩男角定女角？可唔可以重設？</ins></strong><br />\nA：隨個人喜好，有整容券買但唔可以改名(購買次數有上限)。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：特典邊度拎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：係屋仔問管家貓揀追加內容。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：再開新角色，之前beta報酬同特典有冇得再拎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：有。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點搵集會區域號碼？</ins></strong><br />\nA：禁option之後禁三角(成員清單)。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：傷害數字可唔可以整走？</ins></strong><br />\nA：設定有得整走。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：鎖定有冇得用3DS果種？</ins></strong><br />\nA：設定有得整。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解用網捉唔到龍？</ins></strong><br />\nA：請盡快做完自由任完成新手教學。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點令條龍撞牆？</ins></strong><br />\nA：確保投石器有裝石仔，飛翔爪上頭對牆R2。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：連線打同solo打有咩分別？</ins></strong><br />\nA：solo 1倍血，2人1.6倍血，3~4人2.5倍血。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解入唔到某啲朋友開嘅任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：低進度入唔到高進度個任，要先觸發劇情，搵到見到條龍，可以發出SOS訊號既位，之後quit任再重開就可以一齊玩。亦都可以等低進度果個睇完cut scene，其他朋友就可以係外面任務板join番。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：我想問某種素材點有？</ins></strong><br />\nA：獵人嘅萬能圖鑑可以幫到你，再唔係問埋個位係農場旁邊位師傅睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：啲調查任點出架，仲有邊到開架？</ins></strong><br />\nA：調查任係打完隻怪就會出（細怪都會），而開任就要先去1樓調查資源管理所（3人組）登錄任務，每個任都有金、銀或者銅嘅特別獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：雌火龍????個任點做？</ins></strong><br />\nA：周圍探索搵雌火龍????痕跡，夠一半佢會叫你返去打一隻蠻顎，打完搵埋剩返果半，儲夠就開櫻火。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咁搵啲痕跡有無得快d既方法？</ins></strong><br />\nA：有，佢出既位其實得幾個點，你自己記得左，搵完無即退任重開。當然你要先入一次記低。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：Juno係咩？</ins></strong><br />\nA：滅盡龍，你試下連續讀100次，愈讀愈快就會知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點開麒麟任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：係你打完下位風漂龍之後，去生物學者個邊接自由任。第一個自由任係兩星嘅捕捉搔鳥，打完再返去生物學者接下一個自由任。跟住重覆步驟，捉土砂龍，浮空龍。直到捉埋慘爪龍，就接到個麒麟任。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咁上位嘅麒麟任呢？</ins></strong><br />\nA：主線打完古龍之後去珊瑚台地8區同12區到搵佢啲痕跡，搵到某個程度就開比你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：上下位G位/&alpha;&beta;&gamma;混裝出唔出到套裝技？</ins></strong><br />\nA：可以，套裝技能名相同就得。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解開唔到爛輝/赤龍任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：任務限時開放，請留意官網，開放時於集會區域承接。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解連唔到線？</ins></strong><br />\nA：因為要俾錢買PS Plus。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：冇香港PSN，係咪要買多次？</ins></strong><br />\nA：唔需要，可以開個香港account set常用ps4就可以用有買嘅account玩。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：有無人開個新手群？</ins></strong><br />\nA：冇，有嘢請直接問。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解唔整TG GP？</ins></strong><br />\nA：因為無必要，有咩想問有怪想打，係呢度出句聲，大把巴絲打答你幫你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：最頂張圖個D咩人黎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：三百蚊得4條龍，佢地冇買到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>攻略 IB前 PC玩家適用</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/nGNGQFX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/nGNGQFX</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><ins>攻略 IB後</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">魔物篇</span><br />\n赤龍攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/nGNGRgX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/nGNGRgX</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n新Post Template:<br />\n右上角三粒點＞以此內容建立新主題"},{"pid":"89b3081178caece6a98d6f5ec89e10f14f22a484","tid":1984730,"uid":173540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"準備恥笑要刷M位爛輝既人"},{"pid":"551e6ff74029bd0c50862ca4a698f8ecac93a33d","tid":1984730,"uid":3419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615174022a5a4fb4aecc15739e5b7ccfc467a106","tid":1984730,"uid":85909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27689f3f929a8fe35bc0c74bf4b993d933078718","tid":1984730,"uid":123503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"063704406d42321eee5dd0b4a354932bbe525972","tid":19